  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK127">
<l>yākāvā rāyiṉu nākākka kāvākkāṟ</l>
<l>cōkāppar colliḻukkup paṭṭu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though they beware nought else, let them beware their words, lest unawares</l>
<l>they fall into the woes that come from wicked speech.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
